metadata.name: lying woman 1
metadata.description: before going to bed she took a shower, wrapped the towel around her hair so she wouldn't wet the pillow, asked her if she would pose for a drawing and excitingly she said yes but I'll be reading on my phone replied afterwards, and she fell asleep soon after I started....this is a drawing of the woman without any boundaries  and judgment, without the existence of anything between the viewer and the lying woman.
